 254:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c.c ****      The compilation flag USE_HAL_I2C_REGISTER_CALLBACKS when set to 1
 255:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c.c ****      allows the user to configure dynamically the driver callbacks.
 256:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c.c ****      Use Functions HAL_I2C_RegisterCallback() or HAL_I2C_RegisterAddrCallback()
 257:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c.c ****      to register an interrupt callback.
